---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - BurnXLabs" description="Learn about BurnXLabs, the team behind BurnX AI fitness coaching app designed for beginners.">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="pt-16 pb-20 px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                Building the future of beginner fitness
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                We're on a mission to make fitness accessible to everyone, starting with those who need it most - complete beginners.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        At BurnXLabs, we believe everyone deserves access to personalized fitness guidance, regardless of their experience level or background.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        Traditional fitness apps assume you already know what you're doing. They throw complex workouts at you, use confusing terminology, and expect you to keep up. We're different.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                        BurnX is built from the ground up for people who are just starting their fitness journey. Our AI coach understands that you might not know what a "superset" is, or how to properly do a push-up. And that's perfectly okay.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-pink-50 rounded-2xl p-12 text-center">
                    <div class="text-6xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-pink-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">
                        500K+
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">
                        People want to start their fitness journey but don't know where to begin
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values Section -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-16">Our Values</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Accessibility First</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                        Fitness should be for everyone. We remove barriers, simplify complexity, and make starting easy.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-pink-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-pink-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Empathy Driven</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                        We understand the fear and uncertainty of starting. Our approach is encouraging, never intimidating.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Progress Powered</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                        Small wins lead to big changes. We celebrate every step forward, no matter how small.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Section -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Meet the Team</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    A passionate group of fitness enthusiasts, AI engineers, and designers working to democratize fitness.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Team Member 1 -->
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-blue-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6"></div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Sarah Chen</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">CEO & Co-founder</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                        Former Google AI researcher passionate about making technology more human-friendly.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Team Member 2 -->
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-400 to-pink-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6"></div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Marcus Johnson</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">CTO & Co-founder</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                        Ex-Apple engineer who believes great technology should feel magical, not complicated.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Team Member 3 -->
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-green-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6"></div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Dr. Emily Rodriguez</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Head of Fitness Science</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                        Sports scientist dedicated to evidence-based fitness that works for real people.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Story Section -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">Our Story</h2>
            <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto text-gray-600">
                <p class="mb-6">
                    BurnXLabs started with a simple observation: millions of people want to get fit, but the fitness industry isn't built for beginners.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-6">
                    Our founder, Sarah, watched her mom struggle with fitness apps that assumed she knew how to do a burpee or what HIIT meant. 
                    Apps that made her feel inadequate instead of empowered. That's when she realized technology could do better.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-6">
                    Partnering with Marcus and Dr. Emily, they set out to build something different. An AI fitness coach that remembers what it's 
                    like to be a beginner. One that explains things clearly, adapts to your pace, and celebrates your progress.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Today, we're building BurnX to be the fitness companion we wish existed when we started our own journeys. 
                    Because everyone deserves to feel confident, capable, and supported on their path to better health.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-pink-500">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                Ready to start your fitness journey?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-10">
                Join thousands waiting for the fitness app that finally gets beginners.
            </p>
            <a href="/#waitlist" class="bg-white text-gray-900 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors inline-block">
                Join the Waitlist
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>